Package eu.advance.logistics.flow.engine.xml.typesystem

The XML type-system related classes, the XElement parser and the SchemaParser classes.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    XComparable<T>
    The comparison interface for two types.
    XSemantics
    The interface to declare a semantic token.
    XSerializable
    Common interface to denote objects which can be serialized and deserialized into XElements.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SchemaParser
    A XML type description.
    UriSemantics
    A basic URI semantics with only equivalence relation.
    URLResolver
    Utility class to resolve XML schemas relative to a base URL.
    XCapability
    The XML capability description, basically the class field description.
    XElement
    A simplified XML element model.
    XElement.XAttributeName
    The namespace:name record.
    XElement.XRepresentationRecord
    The representation record.
    XGenerics
    The generic type information of an XType.
    XName
    The XML naming record.
    XNavigator
    An implementation for Jaxen's XPath engine.
    XSerializables
    Utility classes to handle XSerializable object creation and conversion.
    XType
    The definition of an XML type: basically a root element or an element with complex type.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    XCardinality
    The cardinality enum for an element.
    XElement.XRepresentationState
    The representation state.
    XRelation
    The relation indicator.
    XValueType
    The enumeration for simple XML value types.
